{"tid":2048244,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"比個鼻搞到就黎想自殺","createTime":"2020-06-02T15:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T04:45:58.000Z","uid":61974,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"88fb04ef3667279e60d2938e906b8b7b67d94f3b","tid":2048244,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T15:55:39.000Z","msg":"平時會好多痰，個鼻有時好乾，好似失左咗自潔能力咁<br />\n<br />\n啲痰係好稠濃，朝早半夜都會比痰札醒，嚴重起上黎訓唔到，平時要靠鹽水洗鼻舒緩<br />\n<br />\n維持左兩年幾，病情反反覆覆時好時壞，睇過專科照過內鏡，話有炎症，開啲化痰藥同比咗鼻眼適我噴，都係冇幫助<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都試過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be019d4c32d8bd4e90177045ac4c62e6abdffd67","tid":2048244,"uid":47658,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個鼻有痰"},{"pid":"f4d9aca3ed3af2ce6995954e842c5dd12c97a2ec","tid":2048244,"uid":302151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:00:57.000Z","msg":"有咩game可以沉迷下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888b2bb1554196543092d76e854fc283210725a2","tid":2048244,"uid":271420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"轉下醫生睇下？"},{"pid":"22aee809a4e5ef441d1a0b4394872e7a5520f1c6","tid":2048244,"uid":143483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"有冇洗鼻 <br />\n訓覺環境點樣<br />\n空氣要流通"},{"pid":"f9edbbd4a168a1c6ae2c9c9041af2d7e93f3cde5","tid":2048244,"uid":1095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:03:25.000Z","msg":"食藥<br />\n自己試吓邊種藥work (鼻敏感藥有好多種<br />\n出邊啲醫生開嚟開去通常都係同一隻 eg loratadine <br />\n<br />\n另外吸多啲塵，買部空氣清新機都有幫助"},{"pid":"745c0c6aa138a5ef7eec75f72983f41e10dc839a","tid":2048244,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"888b2bb1554196543092d76e854fc283210725a2","tid":2048244,"uid":271420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"轉下醫生睇下？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"諗緊睇唔睇中醫"},{"pid":"97c5c52fbacc93c0c86d04bef652fd0d8ceb9b53","tid":2048244,"uid":1095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be019d4c32d8bd4e90177045ac4c62e6abdffd67","tid":2048244,"uid":47658,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個鼻有痰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"通常係鼻水倒流"},{"pid":"7985ebe63cdf1cc796093b570cd2e21abdca4742","tid":2048244,"uid":127331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:05:04.000Z","msg":"你用邊隻洗鼻<br />\n用唔岩方法洗鼻有機會令炎症難好<br />\n專科呢個唔得就睇第2個啦<br />\n個個醫生都有唔同做法"},{"pid":"931b64cd457d8204a72d506e7a04a6d404389fa6","tid":2048244,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22aee809a4e5ef441d1a0b4394872e7a5520f1c6","tid":2048244,"uid":143483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"有冇洗鼻 <br />\n訓覺環境點樣<br />\n空氣要流通"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"日日鹽水洗鼻，仲要係美國啲專用既洗鼻鹽"},{"pid":"da8b75ae0a60f3e2a8f2ddcdc12663d347e3d885","tid":2048244,"uid":143483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"931b64cd457d8204a72d506e7a04a6d404389fa6","tid":2048244,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22aee809a4e5ef441d1a0b4394872e7a5520f1c6","tid":2048244,"uid":143483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"有冇洗鼻 <br />\n訓覺環境點樣<br />\n空氣要流通"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"日日鹽水洗鼻，仲要係美國啲專用既洗鼻鹽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:06:24.000Z","msg":"做運動 每日20分鐘有氧"},{"pid":"040cc4e4747279d791cef7a755ed0688176b5af9","tid":2048244,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7985ebe63cdf1cc796093b570cd2e21abdca4742","tid":2048244,"uid":127331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T16:05:04.000Z",